				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><table class="infobox biography vcard" cellspacing="3" style="border-spacing: 3px; width:22em;">
<tr>
<th colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; font-size:125%; font-weight:bold;"><span class="fn">Charles Henry Holden</span></th>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Charles_Holden_by_Benjamin_Nelson.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/11/Charles_Holden_by_Benjamin_Nelson.jpg/220px-Charles_Holden_by_Benjamin_Nelson.jpg" width="220" height="155" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/11/Charles_Holden_by_Benjamin_Nelson.jpg/330px-Charles_Holden_by_Benjamin_Nelson.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/11/Charles_Holden_by_Benjamin_Nelson.jpg/440px-Charles_Holden_by_Benjamin_Nelson.jpg 2x" /></a><br />
